            "text_7PcwMY": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Milton’s Popcorn was born in the rolling hills of Central Pennsylvania, right in the heart of Dutch Country—where good food, family, and honest craftsmanship are a way of life. From the start, our mission was simple: make popcorn that feels homemade, tastes incredible, and brings people together.<br/></p><p>We spent years sampling recipes, tweaking flavors, and selecting only the best ingredients—including premium mushroom popcorn, the best grade of brown sugar and real butter for our caramel, premium cheddar cheeses, and rich, flavorful coatings to create a variety of flavors. Every handful had to be something we were proud to share. That dedication paid off—one small batch at a time.</p>",
