            "text_gYVgw3": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>For over three decades, we’ve kept things personal—popping in small batches, never cutting corners, and always staying true to the craft. Learning as we go. Along the way, we’ve had the joy of serving millions of happy popcorn lovers from all across Pennsylvania, the northeast, and the mid-Atlantic.</p><p>Then, in 2026, after 31 years in the popcorn business, Milton’s decided it was time to expand westward and into the heart of popcorn country. In doing so, we brought creative recipes into Milton's kitchen—combining our tradition with Rocky Mountain flair. </p>",
