                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Every batch of Milton’s Popcorn begins with premium ingredients and a dedication to doing things the right way. We use top-grade mushroom kernels for their perfect pop and crunch, then coat each batch with a variety of seasonings. Using real butter, pure cane sugar, and rich, savory cheeses to create flavors that feel homemade yet unforgettable.</p><p>Popped in small batches and packed fresh, every flavor captures the warmth, care, and craftsmanship that define Milton’s. From sweet caramel to bold cheddar, our popcorn is crafted to deliver pure joy—bite after bite.</p>",
